      "category": "Industry",
      "description": "In this post, we show you how PAR built a production-ready multi-tenant LLM analytics system that enforces row-level security through a three-layer architecture: cryptographic request signing with AWS SigV4, semantic validation on Amazon Bedrock, and programmatic data isolation via Split-Plane SQL. We demonstrate how each layer operates independently to reduce the risk of cross-tenant data exposure, even when the LLM itself is compromised or manipulated.",
